      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING ZEPPELIN (4) turned heads when clocking a flying 29.68 over 520m at Wentworth Park. In form and rates on top again. GUDRID (8) has been out of the placings last two but prior to that posted a fast 29.83 win over 520m at Wentworth Park. Top win three back and can measure up again. BIG TOWN TILLY (1) was sent out long odds last time but charged out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 4 length fourth (29.93) over 520m at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. In the mix. HELLO HOW LOW (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
